description: Demolition of existing buildings and structures and redevelopment to provide a campus of seven buildings from one to nine storeys in height providing 139 residential units, a new building for Mildmay Hospital (2,795 sq m), a new building for the Shoreditch Tabernacle Baptist Church (423 sq m), a commercial unit (72 sq m) (Use Classes A1-A4 or B1) fronting onto Hackney Road, new landscape amenity areas, parking, servicing and cycle bay provision, highway works and all necessary enabling works.
